OL,6,     FThe Big Job: Wolfie owes Harry
OL,7,     FFenning a hundred pounds for
OL,8,     Fdamaging the pool table in his
OL,9,     Fpub, so Harry devises a way Wolfie
OL,10,     Fcan work off the debt.
OL,11,G0415 Citizen Smith
OL,12,     FTofkin's Revenge: Wolfie is
OL,13,     Fapproached by PC Tofkin, who, in
OL,14,     Freturn for keeping quiet about
OL,15,     FWolfie's antics, wants help to get
OL,16,     Frevenge on Harry Fenning.
OL,17,G0445 Citizen Smith
OL,18,     FWe Shall Not Be Moved: When Dad
OL,19,     Fevicts Ken and Wolfie, they sneak
